          "process_md": "&gt; **Registration Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Go to the [official website](https://www.tribal.mp.gov.in/) of the Tribal Welfare Department of Madhya Pradesh.\n**Step 2:** On the home page, click on ‘[MPTAASC](https://www.tribal.mp.gov.in/MPTAAS)’.\n**Step 3:** Click on &amp;quot;[New Beneficiary Profile Registration](https://www.tribal.mp.gov.in/PMS/Registration/BeneficiaryRegistration/PersonalDetail)&amp;quot; under the ‘Login’ section.\n**Step 4:** Complete all mandatory fields marked with * and upload the required documents.\n**Step 5:** Review your details and click &amp;quot;Submit.&amp;quot;\n**Step 6:** After submission, check your email and SMS for your user ID and password.\n&gt; **Application Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Revisit the [official website](https://www.tribal.mp.gov.in/) of the Tribal Welfare Department of Madhya Pradesh.\n**Step 2:** On the home page, click on ‘[MPTAASC](https://www.tribal.mp.gov.in/MPTAAS)’.\n**Step 3:** Enter your user ID, password, and captcha code, then click &amp;quot;Login.&amp;quot;\n**Step 4:** On the dashboard, click &amp;quot;PMS&amp;quot; and then select &amp;quot;Apply for Scheme.&amp;quot;\n**Step 5:** Fill out the online application form, upload the necessary documents, and submit it.\n**Step 6:** After successful submission, print a copy of the application for your records. \n**Note 1:** It is mandatory for the applicant to register the beneficiary profile.\n**Note 2:** Current status information is sent to the registered email and SMS.\n**Note 3:** The process of approval, acceptance, and payment under the scheme is done online through the [MPTAAS portal.](https://www.tribal.mp.gov.in/MPTAAS)\n"
        }
